{
  "stem": "11998.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And then the last guy, he noticed the hatch in the ceiling.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And he started saying, is there anybody there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And of course, nobody answers, then he started shooting right through the ceiling.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And the women started screaming.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And so we had to open it up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And we went out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And as we were walking down, the same guy was very meticulous, and he must have seen a crack of light between-- because it was getting dark already in the corridor-- it was lighter in the roof space-- he saw a crack of light between the box and the opening.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "So he forcibly got everybody out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And he shot into the space to make people come out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "So everybody left with us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "As far as I know, the space in the basement, they didn't find.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And I found out subsequently many years later, that the people did survive in there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "But then they give themselves up because there was nothing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "There was no food, and the Nazis were all over the place.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "So they were actually kept there, and they were working and liquidating the ghetto-- removing all the valuables from the ghetto and et cetera.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, as I said, we worked, and I worked in the shoe factory.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I had a very good rapport with the son, who was a [NON-ENGLISH], who was running this plant.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was a very rough guy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A national German.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was living in Poland but he was and national German.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they, of course, assumed their heritage, and they became the overseers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They became the people who looked after, when the Jewish business was taken over, they became the [? tri-handler, ?] which would mean the third hand.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
